Usage: releasify draft [--path|-p <path>] [--semver|s <relese>] [--tag|-t <pattern>] [--help|-h]
  print out the new version that should be released with its changelog

  -p, --path <path>
      The path to the project to release. Default `pwd`

  -t, --tag <pattern>
      The pattern of the tag to release. Useful for multi-branch project. Default `v*`

  -s, --semver <release>
      Force the release type. The value must be major, premajor, minor, preminor, patch, prepatch, or prerelease

  -h, --help
      Show this help message